# Agent 4 — Gate Enforcement (Backend + Discord)

You wire the ConfluenceGate into every path that emits a signal. Fix the bypass holes.
**BLOCKED until Agent 2 delivers `intraday_snapshot.json`.** Start only when `/tmp/intraday_snapshot.json` exists.

