- ❌ Do NOT make thesis check optional or configurable. It's always on during market hours.
- ❌ Do NOT catch and silently swallow the thesis blocking. It must return `blocked=True`.
- ❌ Do NOT modify frontend files. Backend + Discord only.
- ❌ Do NOT remove or weaken existing Gate 1 (REGIME) or Gate 2 (BIAS).
- ✅ If `/tmp/intraday_snapshot.json` doesn't exist, pass (no penalty). Don't crash.
- ✅ Gate 0 only applies when `market_open=True`. Pre/post market = pass through.

